                    <div class="text-center">
                        <p class="MsoNormal">About TALENTJET</p>

                        <p class="MsoNormal"> TALENTJET, popularly known as the ultimate model factory, is a 
                            platform where models are trained, groomed and prepared for shining in the 
                            glamour industry. The literal meaning of model that signifies a person with 
                            ideal qualities who can be considered the best to follow while pursuing fashion 
                            trends. TALENTJET thus strives to prepare these models to their best. According 
                            to them, a model shouldn’t be a person with just good looks and figure, but they 
                            should also possess ideal style of walking, speaking and communicating. These 
                            trends together in a person make up a good model. With the detailed research and 
                            analysis, TALENTJET prepares the best models and launches them into the glamour 
                            industry every year.</p>
                        <p class="MsoNormal">
                            <p>&nbsp;</p>
                        </p>
                        <p class="MsoNormal">This is why we are here</p>
                        <p class="MsoNormal">
                            Founded in the year 2013, by Mr.Om Swarup Bindhani with a vision of producing 
                            better models into the glamour world and taking the concept of modelling to the 
                            next level through the concept of ethical modelling, it has created a lots of 
                            opportunities for budding models in the past and is marching ahead with its pace 
                            to crave out paths to glory for potential models. Having catered to the needs of 
                            models for branding, advertisements and shows of several elite corporates, 
                            TALENTJET has established deep connections with them and is considered to be full 
                            of carrier opportunities for budding models having the zeal to grow and prosper. 
                            The major USP of TALENTJET is that unlike many other modelling platforms that 
                            simply acts as a coordinating platform between models and the companies that 
                            require them, it acts as a platform where models are groomed, taught proper 
                            skills that an ideal model should possess and brush them up to shine in the 
                            glamour world.</p>
                        <p class="MsoNormal">
                            <p>&nbsp;</p>
                        </p>
                        <p class="MsoNormal">
                            We Make A Difference</p>
                        <p class="MsoNormal">
                            Our model training and nurturing systems are well analysed and researched and 
                            implemented to produce the best possible versions of the models who register in 
                            our portal for pursuing a career in the modelling industry. With us being in the 
                            industry, the aspiring models don’t have to go through all that struggle and 
                            hustle that comes their way when trying to build a career in this industry. 
                            There are many unethical modelling agencies in the market who misguide young 
                            models and make them spend lots for just getting auditioned. We believe in 
                            ethical modelling and act as the best platform where models can nurture their 
                            talents and climb the ladder of success in modelling career.</p>
